sentences: Geir "Gerlioz" Bratland (born 29 July 1970 in Narvik, Norway) is a Norwegian keyboardist for the band Dimmu Borgir (2010-) and formerly was a member of  the bands God Seed, Apoptygma Berzerk, The Kovenant, and Satyricon.
